&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: #555753; font-family: 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 20px;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Jul 2011 17:35:03 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/%C2%BFsabes-para-donde-va-tu-dinero</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/%C2%BFsabes-para-donde-va-tu-dinero</guid></item></channel></rss>